<item>
            <title>[HBASE-83] Add JMeter performance test for HBase</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-83</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PerformanceEvaluation test is good for running benchmarks, but is not really designed for learning about the performance of HBase for real world datasets. By using JMeter we can test HBase to discover its average response time under different loads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
